HEADWORD: Alitrunk
<hw>Al"i*trunk</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ala</ets> wing + <ets>truncus</ets> trunk.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The segment of the body of an insect to which
